timelineItems.text: 78': GOAL, Ethan Finlay. That's number 10 for him and there's not time to celebrate -- he rushes the ball to midfield w/ #Crew96 down 2-1.

timelineItems.text: When the #Crew96 were down 2-0, I said to myself, "I wonder if Eddie Gaven is available." Unreal that we do it again - without him. :-)
